Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:29.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not moving, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:34.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,If I do, you mean to go away for good, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're going to run off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:41.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you planning on leaving everyone and everything behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:48.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Sorry. I can't be here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:53.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Since when did you become such a coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:59.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Where's the guy that told me "nothing good comes out of being afraid"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:04.66,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,What the hell are you guys doing this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.41,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Richie-rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.02,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:18.96,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,So you two were fighting about the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I understand that you're really into it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:25.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,The truth is I was scared too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:32.60,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:37.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Let me stay like this... just for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.42,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Ritsuko! Did you bring in today's paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:47.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah! I left it by the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.49,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.71,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.15,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,It's Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.34,Main Dialog,Taichi,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:05.47,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.64,Main Dialog,Taichi,0,0,0,,Did you bring us anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.04,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,Dad, your hair's turned gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.31,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Has it? I suppose it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.62,Main Dialog,Taichi,0,0,0,,Did you bring presents?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:15.31,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,I bought some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.31,Main Dialog,Taichi,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.29,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,Let's have 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.41,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Hey, at least let him set foot in the house first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.40,Main Dialog,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H293030&\bord0\shad0\fnaugie\frx10\fry332\frz7.083\blur0.65\pos(462,187)}Welcome{\alpha&HFF&} Home, Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.40,Main Dialog,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H293030&\bord0\shad0\fnaugie\frx10\fry332\frz7.083\blur0.65\alpha&HFF&\pos(748,225)}Welcome{\alpha&H00&} Home{\alpha&HFF&}, Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.40,Main Dialog,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fnaugie\frx10\fry332\frz7.083\blur0.65\alpha&HFF&\pos(532,733)\c&H1E2325&}Welcome Home,{\alpha&H00&} Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:27.28,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Everyone, I'm sorry for being away all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.24,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,You look cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.21,Main Dialog,Taichi,0,0,0,,Look, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:34.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,That's great, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.12,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:39.38,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,is for you, Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:46.41,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Um... I don't know if you'll like it or not, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:56.39,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,It's a fountain pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.14,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,You're lucky, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:58.90,Main Dialog,Taichi,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:02.90,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Something expensive like this is wasted on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:07.91,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,A child doesn't go turning down a present from his parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:14.24,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, looks like everyone got a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:16.25,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,Sachiko, pass these out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.15,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:27.13,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,A child. His parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you coming to practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah. Startin' today, I'm gonna practice my ass off for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.28,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:56.52,Main Dialog,Man,0,0,0,,What the hell? That was a weird way to greet to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:00.92,Main Dialog,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H486899&\bord0\blur.75\fax-.1\shad0\frx16\fry334\frz7.732\pos(818,523)\blur.5}Mukae
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.92,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Me, at the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was hoping that you would play bass for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.88,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,You're asking me out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.79,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Adults have a lot of things on their plate, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:13.36,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,And there'd be so much to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:14.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,So you can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:27.15,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,You're totally prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Ain't no way we can lose now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.55,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.84,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,How's it goin' for you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.68,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,We're getting our costumes fitted right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:58.81,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,There's no way we're going to lose to you guys this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's so flamboyant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:03.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,We, on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,are plain. Way too plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:11.63,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,We don't have any razzmatazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,We might not be able to beat them like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:16.76,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,That stuff doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:19.66,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,All we gotta do is put our music face-to-face against theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I know! I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:27.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,But this is our last school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:29.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I just don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.51,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Easy to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:36.87,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,But appealing to people who have no interest in jazz is a tall order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.81,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I can't sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:53.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't worry. There are still ten days left. We'll work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.57,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko, if you're gonna refuse, now's the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:00.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,'Cause if you decide to do it, we're not gonna go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:03.13,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,You don't wanna sing, tell us to shove off right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:08.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I hope you don't turn us down, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:09.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I agree with Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Would you help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.88,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,All right. I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:35.26,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:44.79,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kit-tens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No, you've got no swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:57.21,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:00.85,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Bright copper kettles and warm woolen mittens
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:04.66,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Brown paper packages tied up with strings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:08.19,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:12.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Cream colored ponies and crisp apple strudels
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:15.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Doorbells and sleigh bells and schnitzel with noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:19.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Wild geese that fly with the moon on their wings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.91,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:26.62,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Girls in white dresses with blue satin sashes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:30.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Snowflakes that stay on my nose and eyelashes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:34.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Silver white winters that melt into springs
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:37.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:47.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I simply remember my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:55.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,And then I don't feel so bad
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:02.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,"My Favorite Things," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,My {\i1}own{\i0\fscx150} {\fscx100}favorite things are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:08.82,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,The footsteps of a certain person heading towards the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:12.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,The sound of the piano and drums in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:14.98,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,The laughter of two boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Silly, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:24.05,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Drums and watermelon and onigiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:27.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,These are a few of my favorite things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:31.17,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What the heck was that, Sentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:32.82,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Go on, Richie. Your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:36.26,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Tell us your "favorite things."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I don't have any!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Even before Ri said hers, I had something in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:47.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Right now, my favorite thing is this very moment. {orig: my favorite thing is this time... right now}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:00.87,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:03.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,All that's left is to play our best at the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:07.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, how about playin' "Moanin'" one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Nah, let's save it for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.65,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,If we started jamming now, we wouldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I see. Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well, see you tomorrow then. Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.35,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,He forget to take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:33.39,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, you don't need a score for jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:35.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I can just give it to him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.63,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.39,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm gonna run to deliver something he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.55,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,He left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:48.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You might not be able to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.84,Main Dialog,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H232521&\bord0\shad0\blur0.75\fax0.1\fs50\frz348.8\frx10\fry16\pos(442,292)}19th {\bord1\3c&H44416A&\c&H726AC8&}School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:22.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen's awfully late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.22,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.64,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,It's almost time for our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.26,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he's late?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.14,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Seiji, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:36.06,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Okay! Well, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.08,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.54,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,He was in a motorcycle accident last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,and was taken to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:00.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,S-So how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.30,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I don't know! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.01,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.64,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro is... Sentaro is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the hospital and see how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Stay here until I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:19.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:24.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I've ran down this slope countless times, but it's never felt this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:29.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm looking for—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:33.29,Main Dialog,Woman,0,0,0,,I'll help you when it's your turn, so please get in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:35.83,Main Dialog,Woman,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I heard there was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:59.23,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,They've finished operating, but there was serious head trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.44,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,Still hasn't regained consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:08.28,Main Dialog,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H222115&\bord0\b1\shad0\fnCalligraph421 BT\fs33\blur0.5\move(637,142,637,121,0,4531)\t(\fs36)}No Visitors
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:08.28,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,Might never wake up again... The doctor said... {i dont like this but its hard to leave out the pronoun otherwise}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:10.16,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.41,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:19.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's right! Even when Sen is all bloody from a fight, he just laughs it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:26.42,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,Um... Sachiko is the one who's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:34.89,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but she was riding on the back of Bro's bike last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.60,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,They got hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Then how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.86,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,He's hurt, but not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.57,Main Dialog,Kota,0,0,0,,He was sitting over here just a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I see. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:58.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's right! The place he's most likely to go has...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,got to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.90,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I've seen this angel before somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:14.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,If you're gonna take somebody to Heaven, could you make it me an' not Sachiko, angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:25.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Why do I end up hurting the ones I most want to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:33.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Why was I even born?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.18,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you cryin' for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:53.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,This way, we don't have to see each other cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,What do you mean "we"? I ain't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.16,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's okay to cry, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:05.08,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You've been keeping it bottled up all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:46.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.30,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh? Sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:05.23,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,At the time, it looked like he was just stepping out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:12.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but he disappeared, and the festival ended before it even began.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.78,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.45,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:24.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um, here. If you're able to eat these...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.54,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Do you know where Sen went?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:32.88,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,He would normally never give me a ride on his bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:39.18,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,But I had a twisted ankle and kept complaining about it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:42.43,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,The accident was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.77,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,I have to apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:50.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sa, just focus on getting better for right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sentaro will be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:56.03,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You want to show him that you're healthy again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:57.82,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:07.79,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I said all of that to her, but the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:14.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, what'll I do if he never comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:16.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,We're talking about {\i1}him{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:23.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I bet he'll turn up when we're least expecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't you have that feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.93,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll come back, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:31.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:35.65,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, don't go anywhere, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:41.66,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:47.58,Main Dialog,Priest,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember you. Richie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.08,Main Dialog,Priest,0,0,0,,Do I know where he might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:54.79,Main Dialog,Priest,0,0,0,,No, I'm afraid I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:20:00.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um... Father, he left this behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:07.89,Main Dialog,Priest,0,0,0,,He once told me the reason he always wore the rosary as a necklace was because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:15.44,Main Dialog,Priest,0,0,0,,he was afraid that if he lost it, he would be abandoned by the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.72,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Se—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:51.18,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,I thought maybe Sen had come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:21:00.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Pops... He's not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:05.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll never be able to practice with him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:08.74,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talkin' about, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Never again.
